name: Letter O
description:
“Letters” Collection by Simay Fidan

Architect and designer Simay Fidan designed this collection as an expression of personal experience of emotion and symbolism. Stemming from her interest in letterforms and typography led her to design this series of artworks of 22 different letters. Each color and letter represent different emotions that she has had through her life based on memories of individuals and events forever preserved here as the “Letters” digital art collection.   

March 2022
Simay Fidan
